45
00:03:13,810 --> 00:03:15,430
and trap her step by step.

46
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:17,840
Her defense will gradually collapse.

47
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,360
This strategy will surely succeed.

48
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:21,560
