111
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,360
The little tiger is me.

112
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,950
The little rabbit is you.

113
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:17,040
Whatever will happen in the future,

114
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:18,660
